{
  "nbformat": 4,
  "nbformat_minor": 5,
  "metadata": {
    "kernelspec": {
      "name": "maxima",
      "display_name": "Maxima",
      "language": "maxima"
    },
    "aximar": {}
  },
  "cells": [
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "# Taylor Series Convergence\n\nThis notebook explores Taylor series through Maxima's **symbolic-numeric bridge**:\nwe derive series expansions symbolically with `taylor()`, then evaluate and plot\nthem numerically to study convergence, accuracy, and the effect of truncation order.\n\nKey Maxima functions: `taylor`, `ratdisrep`, `diff`, `subst`, `float`.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "load(\"numerics\")$\nload(\"ax-plots\")$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 85,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Basic Taylor Expansion\n\nStart with $f(x) = e^x$ and compute its 5th-order Taylor polynomial\naround $x = 0$. The symbolic CAS gives us the exact coefficients;\nthen we plot the polynomial alongside the true function.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Symbolic Taylor expansion of exp(x) to order 5 */\nf : exp(x)$\nT5 : taylor(f, x, 0, 5);\nT5_poly : ratdisrep(T5);",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 86,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "1+x+x^2/2+x^3/6+x^4/24+x^5/120"
          ]
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "text/latex": [
              "{{x^5}\\over{120}}+{{x^4}\\over{24}}+{{x^3}\\over{6}}+{{x^2}\\over{2}}+x+1"
            ]
          },
          "execution_count": 86,
          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "execute_result"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Compare exp(x) and its 5th-order Taylor polynomial */\nax_draw2d(\n  color=blue, name=\"exp(x)\",\n  explicit(exp(x), x, -4, 4),\n  color=red, dash=\"dash\", name=\"Taylor O(5)\",\n  explicit(T5_poly, x, -4, 4),\n  title=\"exp(x) vs Taylor Polynomial (order 5)\",\n  yrange=[-1, 20], grid=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 87,
      "outputs": [
        {
